Package bt.protocol.extended

Class ExtendedHandshake

  • java.lang.Object
    • bt.protocol.extended.ExtendedMessage
      • bt.protocol.extended.ExtendedHandshake
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Message

    public final class ExtendedHandshake
extends ExtendedMessage
    Extended handshake is sent during connection initialization procedure by peers that support BEP-10: Extension Protocol. It contains a dictionary of supported extended message types with their corresponding numeric IDs, as well as any additional information, that is specific to concrete BitTorrent clients and BEPs, that utilize extended messaging.
    Since:
    1.0
